    "lyrics": {
      "text": "To thee, the Cham-----pion Lead-er,__ we thy flock__ now ded-----i--cate__ a ho-ly feast_____ of great thanks--giv-ing and__ of vic-----to--ry,__ as ones res---cued___ out__ of suf-----f’rings,__ O The-o-to----------kos. But as thou_____ art one with__ might which is__ in-vin-----ci--ble,__ from all dan---gers___ that__ can be_____ do___ thou de-liv--------er__ us, that we may__ cry_______ to__ we__ may cry__ to___ thee:___ Re-joice,______ thou__ pure_____ and___ un---wed--------ded__ Bride______"
    }
